  {%- comment -%} QUOTE INTAKE CHECKLIST (Session B addition) {%- endcomment -%}
  <section class="lp-intake" aria-label="What to include in your quote request">
    <div class="lp-intake__inner">
      <div class="lp-intake__head">
        <p class="lp-intake__eyebrow bbi-mono">Quote intake checklist</p>
        <h2>What to include &mdash; and what we&rsquo;ll ask if it&rsquo;s missing.</h2>
