        <div class="lp-intake__item">
          <span class="lp-intake__num">01</span>
          <div class="lp-intake__body"><strong>Scope summary</strong><p>Line items, headcount, room count, or a one-line description (&ldquo;80 task chairs to standardize a school board&rdquo;).</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-intake__item">
          <span class="lp-intake__num">02</span>
          <div class="lp-intake__body"><strong>Floor plan or measurements (optional)</strong><p>PDF, CAD, or sketch with rough dimensions. We&rsquo;ll free-design a layout for any fit-out above ~6 stations.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-intake__item">
          <span class="lp-intake__num">03</span>
          <div class="lp-intake__body"><strong>OECM membership status</strong><p>Your organization&rsquo;s OECM member number, if you&rsquo;re purchasing under Agreement 2025-470. (Not sure? Call &mdash; we&rsquo;ll confirm in 5 minutes.)</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-intake__item">
          <span class="lp-intake__num">04</span>
          <div class="lp-intake__body"><strong>PO routing details</strong><p>Billing address, PO number format, and any account-setup paperwork your A/P team needs first.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-intake__item">
          <span class="lp-intake__num">05</span>
          <div class="lp-intake__body"><strong>Lead-time window</strong><p>When you need delivery (&ldquo;ASAP&rdquo;, &ldquo;summer install&rdquo;, &ldquo;before Q3&rdquo;). We&rsquo;ll match SKUs to your window.</p></div>
        </div>
        <div class="lp-intake__item">
          <span class="lp-intake__num">06</span>
          <div class="lp-intake__body"><strong>Existing furniture</strong><p>Anything we&rsquo;re replacing, refitting, or working around. We handle removal as a line item if needed.</p></div>
