          <span class="dot"></span>
          <span><b>Ontario-owned &middot; Family-run since 1964.</b> <svg class="bbi-icon bbi-icon--leaf" viewBox="0 0 13 13" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M6.5 0 L7.6 3.5 L11 2 L9 5 L13 6.5 L9.5 7 L11 10.5 L6.5 8.5 L2 10.5 L3.5 7 L0 6.5 L4 5 L2 2 L5.4 3.5 Z"/></svg> Brant Basics OECM 2025-470. Send us a rough scope &mdash; no minimums, no sales pitch.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
