            "answer": "<p>Anything is a starting point — a list of products, a room dimension, a headcount, or links to items you've seen on the site. You don't need a finished floor plan or a confirmed budget to get numbers. We'll ask a few follow-up questions if needed and get you an itemised quote, usually within one business day.</p>"
