          "settings": {
            "question": "What's your typical lead time?",
            "answer": "<p>Lead times vary by manufacturer and configuration. Stock items ship in 1–2 weeks. Custom-build items (configurable seating, build-to-order desks, custom-laminate storage) typically run 6–12 weeks from PO. We flag every line in your quote with its lead time so you can plan around installation windows — particularly important for school summer installs, hospital project deadlines, and end-of-fiscal-year cutoffs.</p>"
